---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Services">
  <main>
    <article>
      <h1>Services</h1>
      <p>
        <a href="/contact">Contact me</a> if you would like to hire me, and we'll
        talk about how I can help.
      </p>

      <h2>Values</h2>
      <p>playfulness, curiosity, simplicity, humility, excellence.</p>

      <br />
      <hr />

      <h2>Software Engineering</h2>
      <p>
        I have 10 years experience and have worked on over 80 client projects.
      </p>
      <p>I am more of a generalist than a specialist.</p>
      <p>
        I normally work as an individual contributor or force multiplier (i.e
        pairing / writing / knowledge production)
      </p>

      <h3>Areas of Experience</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Fullstack web</li>
        <li>Identity (bespoke/Auth0)</li>
        <li>CRM (Salesforce)</li>
        <li>Integration</li>
        <li>APIs</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Languages</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>TypeScript/JS</li>
        <li>Ruby/Rails</li>
        <li>React/Next</li>
        <li>Elm</li>
        <li>Go</li>
        <li>Apex (Salesforce)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Infrastructure</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>AWS</li>
        <li>GCP</li>
        <li>Heroku</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>Music Production / Guitar Lessons</h2>
      I can help you learn guitar, or produce your music.
    </article>
  </main>

  <style>
    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    ul li {
      padding-left: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    ul li::before {
      content: "â€¢";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
    }

    main {
      margin: auto;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 90ch;
      color: #aaaaaa;
    }

    main article {
      font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    main article h1,
    main article h2,
    main article h3 {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    main article h1 {
      color: #eeeeee;
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    main article h2 {
      color: #eeeeee;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    main article h3 {
      color: #eeeeee;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    a {
      color: #f15125;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
